What you need to know:

Apart from Razak, former Sony Sugar tactician Francis Baraza also coaches in Tanzania. Baraza switched from high-flying Biashara United to Kagera Sugar mid this month.Other Kenyans in Tanzanian league are Joash Onyango and Francis Kahata, who both ply their trade with Simba SC.After a three-year drought, Yanga are eying their 28th title and currently lead the Tanzania Premier League table on 50 points after 23 matches, four ahead of reigning champions Simba SC who have three games in hand.Â 